cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.HC 

The paper deals with the application of deep learning techniques to neuroimaging data for the classification of Alzheimer's Disease. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of image entropy to select informative slices for training, which relates to human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
